{"componentChunkName":"component---lib-ui-templates-project-item-tpl-js","path":"/projects/accessible-narrative-text/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>You may be asking yourself \"What is Narrative Text?\"</p>\n<p>It's a fair question and one of those things that when it's explained to you, you instantly realise that you actually knew what it was, but just didn't know what it was called, because it had never cropped up in day-to-day conversation.</p>\n<p><strong>Narrative Text</strong> is text that is displayed over the top of video to describe elements of the story.</p>\n<p>We're working closely with the BBC to take on the challenge of making BBC News' Narrative Text content accessible. BBC News had recently revamped the style and animation of their Narrative Text and wanted to make sure that it not only looked good, but was also accessible to as many people as possible. We replaced the 'burned-in' Narrative Text with the stuff of the web—HTML and CSS.</p>\n<p>Now this text is now accessible by screenreaders, and the visually impaired. Hurrah!</p>","frontmatter":{"active":true,"application":"https://github.com/bbc/newslabs-narrative-text","slides":[{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/93ceb/Screenshot2.png","srcSet":"/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/0fe1a/Screenshot2.png 150w,\n/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/b3c0f/Screenshot2.png 300w,\n/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/93ceb/Screenshot2.png 600w,\n/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/c1d0b/Screenshot2.png 1200w","sizes":"(min-width: 600px) 600px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/fcc64/Screenshot2.webp 150w,\n/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/57091/Screenshot2.webp 300w,\n/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/2f134/Screenshot2.webp 600w,\n/static/3059a9950b2d94ce275d051599087e79/8932d/Screenshot2.webp 12